# Rust build artifacts (the whole workspace builds into the root target/)
/target
**/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Redundant per-member lockfiles: a workspace only uses the root Cargo.lock.
/*/Cargo.lock

# sqlx offline cache (these crates don't use sqlx; kept as a safety net)
.sqlx/

# Local scan state / databases the tools write at runtime
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Secrets / local environment. NEVER commit these, especially in a public repo.
.env
.env.*
*.env

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
